    "A similar form of parallel analysis occurs in the analysis layer.",
    "Our implementation processes subtasks in batches of three to minimize graph recursions while maintaining parallelism within each batch.",
    "Commercial systems likely employ dozens of search agents investigating different research directions simultaneously.Our implementation also demonstrates an important optimization strategy: using different models for different roles.",
